{"word":"H4185 - מוּשׁ - mûwsh - moosh - Cease","slug":"H4185","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מוּשׁ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mûwsh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>moosh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cease"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1; - mu&#x0302;sh</b> - <i>moosh</i><p/>A primitive root (perhaps rather the same as <a href=\"#/H4184\">H4184</a> through the idea of receding by <i>contact</i>); to <i>withdraw</i> (both literally and figuratively, whether intransitively or transitively): - cease, depart, go back, remove, take away."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4171\">H4171</a>, <a href=\"#/H4173\">H4173</a>, <a href=\"#/H4177\">H4177</a>, <a href=\"#/H8545\">H8545</a>"}]}